Few-body interactions constrain entanglement

  • Few-body interactions constrain entanglement
  • yitan@g.harvard.edu
  • Rosetta-Tan
  • Rosetta40235021

SYK model is widely believed to render Page curve, but is that one-hundred percent true? We show that few-body interactions can constrain the entanglement of the system, and the Page curve is not a universal feature of the SYK model.
